databaseoperation.name: gettop10NationalAgencyList1
databaseoperation.sqlstmt: select distinct top 10 obj_code_desc as name from object_code_details where obj_code_desc like '%' +#national_code# + '%' order by obj_code_desc asc

databaseoperation.name: AgenctSavedSearchResult
databaseoperation.sqlstmt: select search_id, search_type, search_name, last_updated_by, last_updated_ts, user_sid, is_global,cast(search_xml as varchar(8000)) as search_xml from savedsearch where search_type = 2 order by search_name asc

databaseoperation.name: contacttype_lku_mom_list_1
databaseoperation.sqlstmt: select contact_typ_id, contact_typ_desc, 0 as isContact from contacttype_lku where applicableto=3 order by contact_typ_desc asc

databaseoperation.name: getDataFromSavedSearch
databaseoperation.sqlstmt: select search_id, search_type, search_name,convert(varchar(8000), search_xml) as search_xml, user_sid,is_global, last_updated_by, last_updated_ts from savedsearch where search_id = #search_id#

databaseoperation.name: getAgencyLobMasterDetailAdvanceSearch
databaseoperation.sqlstmt: select lob_id as agency_lob_id ,lob_code as agency_lob_code,description as agency_lob_desc from lob_lku where description='Commercial Lines' order by description

databaseoperation.name: getSelectedAgencyLobMasterDetail
databaseoperation.sqlstmt: select agency_lob from agency_master where agency_id=#agency_id#

databaseoperation.name: getClosedReasonOther
databaseoperation.sqlstmt: select master_lookup_data_code as custom_reason_code from master_lookup_data_lku where master_lookup_data_id =#closed_reason_code_id#
